quran[26{c,v,t}:
92,15,is mein wohi daakhil ho ga jo bara badbakht hai
92,16,jis ne jhatlaya aur munh phera
92,17,aur jo bara parhaizgaar hai woh ( is se ) bacha liya jaye ga
92,18,jo maal deta hai taakay pak ho
92,19,aur ( is liye ) nahi ( deta ke ) is par kisi ka ahsaan ( hai ) jis ka woh badla utarta hai
92,20,balkay apne khudawand aala ki razamandi haasil karne ke liye deta hai
92,21,aur woh anqareeb khush ho jaye ga
93,1,aftaab ki roshni ki qasam
93,2,aur raat ( ki tareqi ) ki jab chhaa jaye
93,3,ke ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tumahray perwar-digaar ne nah to tum ko chorra aur nah ( tum se ) naraaz howa
93,4,aur akhirat tumahray liye pehli ( haalat yani duniya ) se kahin behtar hai
93,5,aur tumhe perwar-digaar anqareeb woh kuch ataa farmaiye ga ke tum khush ho jao ge
93,6,bhala is ne tumhe yateem pa kar jagah nahi di? ( be shak di )
93,7,aur raste se nawaqif dekha to rasta dekhaya
93,8,aur tang dast paaya to ghanni kar diya
93,9,to tum bhi yateem par sitam nah karna
93,10,aur mangnay walay ko jhirki nah dena
93,11,aur apne perwar-digaar ki nematon ka bayan karte rehna
94,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam )kiya hum ne tumhara seenah khol nahi diya? ( be shak khol diya )
94,2,aur tum par se boojh bhi utaar diya
94,3,jis ne tumhari peeth toar rakhi thi
94,4,aur tumhara zikar bulandkiya
94,5,haan haan mushkil ke sath aasani bhi hai
94,6,( aur ) be shak mushkil ke sath aasani hai
94,7,to jab farigh howa karo to ( ibadat mein ) mehnatkiya karo
94,8,aur apne perwar-digaar ki taraf mutwajjah ho jaya karo
